Mycelium: Deep Analysis Report

What It Is

A git-notes-based knowledge graph for AI agents — one 1661-line bash script (mycelium.sh) with zero dependencies beyond git and bash. Agents read notes on arrival, leave notes on
 departure. Notes attach to commits, files, and directories using structured headers + free-form markdown bodies. Storage is refs/notes/mycelium.

